metadata.name: NFT RAPS - 500Milly
metadata.description:
NFT Raps is the first official music airdrop deployed to holders for free as well as future holders of the No Reddit Genesis Music NFT *While Supply lasts (500 total available) 

This NFT will also be for sale.  Collect a No Reddit Genesis and receive this song for free.  Holding a No Reddit Genesis also makes you eligible for future airdrops and giveaways.  Thank you for supporting my work!

The Art for this music release was created by: @Just_Vixenn - Twitter & IG
